International Ferro Says Quarterly Output Fell 5% After Furnace Roof Leaks

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-04-20T06:15:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/international-ferro-says-quarterly-output-fell-5-after-furnace-roof-leaks.html
  International Ferro Metals Ltd. (IFL) 
said it produced 51,446 metric tons of ferrochrome last quarter,
up 9 percent on the previous quarter and down 5 percent from a
year earlier because of furnace roof leaks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
